### 3-1. 회원 정보 수정 테스트 (닉네임만)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/auth/update
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2Iiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJuYW1lIjoi7LWc7ISx7JqwIiwiZW1haWwiOiJncmVlbnRqZGRuQGdtYWlsLmNvbSIsInByb2ZpbGVJbWFnZVVybCI6IiIsInR5cGUiOiJhY2Nlc3MiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzkzNDUxOTQsImV4cCI6MTc3OTM4ODM5NH0.AytlFMNJai96wIs7rYFK3gj6yXjjUsKp7gJVzeuPGOU
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="data"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "최성후이잉"
}
--WebAppBoundary--

### 3-2. 회원 정보 수정 테스트 (닉네임 + 프로필 이미지)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/auth/update
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2Iiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJuYW1lIjoi7LWc7ISx7JqwIiwiZW1haWwiOiJncmVlbnRqZGRuQGdtYWlsLmNvbSIsInByb2ZpbGVJbWFnZVVybCI6IiIsInR5cGUiOiJhY2Nlc3MiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzkzNDUxOTQsImV4cCI6MTc3OTM4ODM5NH0.AytlFMNJai96wIs7rYFK3gj6yXjjUsKp7gJVzeuPGOU
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="data"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "최성잉"
}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="profileImage"; filename="test-image2.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-image2.png
--WebAppBoundary--
